---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Paid Ads Services — Google, Meta & TikTok | Novelty Ads"
  description="Run high-ROI Google, Meta, and TikTok ads with Novelty Ads. We create data-driven campaigns that drive real leads, best results, and maximum returns for SMBs and startups."
  canonical="https://noveltyads.com/paid-ads-solutions/"
>

<section class="page-hero">
  <div class="container" style="position:relative;z-index:1;">
    <p class="page-hero__eyebrow" data-reveal="up">Paid Advertising</p>
    <h1 class="page-hero__title" data-reveal="up">We're Profitable<br>If You're Profitable.</h1>
    <p class="page-hero__sub" data-reveal="up">High-ROAS paid ad campaigns on Google, Meta, and TikTok. We turn your ad budget into a predictable, scalable revenue machine.</p>
    <div style="display:flex;gap:14px;flex-wrap:wrap;" data-reveal="up">
      <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-yellow btn-lg">Start Your Campaign</a>
      <a href="/case-studies" class="btn btn-outline-white btn-lg">See ROAS Results →</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Platforms -->
<section style="padding:120px 0;background:#F8F7F4;">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:64px;">
      <p class="section-eyebrow eyebrow-dark" data-reveal="up">Ad Platforms</p>
      <h2 class="section-title title-dark" style="margin-top:14px;" data-reveal="up">We run ads where<br>your customers live.</h2>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:14px;" data-stagger>
      <div class="svc-card svc-blue">
        <div class="svc-card__icon">🔵</div>
        <h3 class="svc-card__title">Google Ads</h3>
        <p class="svc-card__desc">Search, Display, Shopping, YouTube, Performance Max. Capture buyers with high intent at the exact moment they're searching for what you offer.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-card svc-orange">
        <div class="svc-card__icon">📘</div>
        <h3 class="svc-card__title">Meta Ads</h3>
        <p class="svc-card__desc">Facebook and Instagram ads that build awareness and drive conversions. Creative strategy, audience targeting, and full-funnel campaign management.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="svc-card svc-purple">
        <div class="svc-card__icon">🎵</div>
        <h3 class="svc-card__title">TikTok Ads</h3>
        <p class="svc-card__desc">Reach the fastest-growing audience. Native-style creative ads that blend into the feed and drive massive reach for emerging brands.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Real results callout -->
<section style="padding:100px 0;background:#0A0A0A;">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:80px;align-items:center;">
      <div data-reveal="up">
        <p class="section-eyebrow eyebrow-light" style="margin-bottom:18px;">Real Campaign Results</p>
        <h2 class="section-title title-light" style="margin-bottom:24px;">What a winning<br>paid ads campaign looks like.</h2>
        <p class="section-sub sub-light" style="margin-bottom:36px;">Our average CPL was ~$38 across Meta & Google. With an Average Order Value of $134, that's a 3.5× ROAS from day one. We optimise until those numbers keep climbing.</p>
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-yellow btn-lg">Get Similar Results →</a>
      </div>
      <div data-reveal="right">
        <div style="background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.1);border-radius:22px;padding:40px;">
          {[
            { label: 'Cost Per Lead (CPL)', val: '~$38', color: '#F5E642' },
            { label: 'Avg. Order Value (AOV)', val: '$134', color: '#05C870' },
            { label: 'Return on Ad Spend', val: '3.5×', color: '#3A5BF0' },
            { label: 'Monthly Ad Managed', val: '$25k+', color: '#FF6B35' },
          ].map(m => (
            <div style="display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;padding:18px 0;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.08);">
              <span style="font-size:14px;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.55);font-weight:500;">{m.label}</span>
              <span style={`font-size:24px;font-weight:800;letter-spacing:-0.03em;color:${m.color};`}>{m.val}</span>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Testimonials -->
<section style="padding:120px 0;background:#F8F7F4;">
  <div class="container">
    <div style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:64px;" data-reveal="up">
      <h2 class="section-title title-dark">What clients say about<br>our paid ad results.</h2>
    </div>
    <div style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:14px;" data-stagger>
      <div class="testi-card testi-blue">
        <div class="testi-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testi-card__quote">"The campaigns generated real, measurable ROI from day one. Usama genuinely cares about results, not just spending your budget."</p>
        <div class="testi-card__author"><div class="testi-avatar">M</div><div><div class="testi-name">Micheal Riley</div><div class="testi-role">Marketing Director</div></div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="testi-card testi-green">
        <div class="testi-card__stars">★★★★★</div>
        <p class="testi-card__quote">"I was impressed with Usama's ability to turn limited resources into effective and engaging social media marketing content that heavily impacted our metrics."</p>
        <div class="testi-card__author"><div class="testi-avatar">J</div><div><div class="testi-name">Jenna Schuchardt</div><div class="testi-role">Marketing Director, Stress Factory</div></div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section style="padding:100px 0 120px;background:#F8F7F4;">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="cta-box" data-reveal="scale">
      <p class="section-eyebrow" style="color:rgba(255,255,255,0.3);margin-bottom:14px;">Launch Your Campaign</p>
      <h2 class="cta-title">Stop guessing.<br>Start scaling.</h2>
      <p class="cta-sub">Book a free paid ads strategy call and get a custom campaign roadmap — no obligations.</p>
      <div class="cta-actions">
        <a href="/contact" class="btn btn-yellow btn-xl">Book Strategy Call →</a>
        <a href="tel:+19292421923" class="btn btn-outline-white btn-xl">📞 Call Us</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

</Layout>
<style>
  @media (max-width:768px) {
    div[style*="grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr)"] { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    div[style*="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr"] { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
    div[style*="grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)"] { grid-template-columns: 1fr !important; }
  }
</style>
